      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "magnitude of a force acting against the enlargement of area portion of a\nsurface separating a liquid from its surrounding\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The concept of ((surface energy)) is closely related to surface tension and\nhas the same dimension.\n",
